{"tid":452564,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"45歲韓星金柱赫遇車禍身亡","createTime":"2017-10-30T10:47:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T02:35:58.000Z","uid":34498,"like":36,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"1f5cd68744a36988bc2fb1f226142454ba858f4e","tid":452564,"uid":34498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:47:20.000Z","msg":"45歲的韓國男演員金柱赫今日下午4時半左右，在首爾江南三成洞附近發生車禍，金柱赫的座駕與另一輛車相撞後，翻下樓梯車輛隨即著火，現場滿地碎片。消防員到達現場後將金柱赫送往醫院，警方確認金柱赫最終不治身亡。<br />\n<br />\n金柱赫有份演出的韓劇《Argon》 ​剛播完，亦曾出演劇集《布拉格戀人》，在《請回答1988》中飾演中年崔澤，在綜藝節目《兩天一夜》中的表現，令他獲得大眾喜愛。另外，去年底他被爆與小17歲女星李宥英因拍戲撻著，雙方的公司也證實戀情，二人曾計劃結婚。"},{"pid":"dad5c1eeda17b40015254d2c00acd6c391782275","tid":452564,"uid":92376,"like":20,"dislike":27,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:48:14.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望連登仔唔好笑.呢個係真男人大叔Oppa類<br />\n唔係果啲男團泡仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a80ec7b0c51bc7fd5d45aa903a12779665aef4","tid":452564,"uid":34498,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:48:48.000Z","msg":"之前見佢上running man仲好活躍 真係人生無常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61066f2979c5569a6a230b99c2e678b0ce872c53","tid":452564,"uid":24034,"like":48,"dislike":27,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:49:17.000Z","msg":"韓狗who fucking cares<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a7d92052efd3e3c709bb229368f6856086c25c","tid":452564,"uid":141551,"like":30,"dislike":37,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:50:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/